HEADWORD: Disturb
<hw>Dis*turb"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Disturbance.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disturbance</ent>⟦br⟧
